We considered two automatic RE tools, Rosette and Diffbot, {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0064||FO}} (Rosette, Diffbot), and three ground truth variants: {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0065||FO}}. For each relation, we report on the combination of RE tool and GT variant that achieves the highest count of documents classified as high-coverage.